text: Maria Alejandra Vicuña (born 13 February 1978) is an Ecuadorean politician. She is the Vice President of Ecuador under President Lenin Moreno from 2 October 2017 until 2018. She also served as the Housing and Urban Development Minister of Ecuador until 6 January 2018. ==Notes== ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Vice presidents of Ecuador Category:Politicians from Guayaquil
title: María Vicuña
